---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
pagination:
  data: posts
  size: 5
  alias: posts
  reverse: false
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="profile-container">
      <div class="profile-image">
        <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/18418340?v=4" alt="Salman Qureshi">
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="site-headline">salmansOpLog</h1>
    <p class="site-description">return myUnfilteredOpinions.filter(thought => thought.isWorthSharing);</p>
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span class="activitypub-badge">@import ActivityPub</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<div class="content-wrapper">
  <main class="posts-container">
    {% for post in pagination.items %}
      <article class="post-card">
        <div class="post-card-content">
          <div class="post-meta">
            <time datetime="{{ post.date }}">{{ post.date | dateToFormat("MMMM d, yyyy") }}</time>
          </div>
          <h2 class="post-title"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.title }}</a></h2>
          <div class="post-excerpt">
            {{ post.excerpt | safe }}
          </div>
          <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">readMore() <span class="arrow">â†’</span></a>
        </div>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
    
    {% include "components/pagination.njk" %}
  </main>

  <aside class="sidebar">
    <div class="about-card">
      <h3>whoami</h3>
      <p>I'm Salman, a developer who spends too much time debugging and not enough time sleeping. These are my unfiltered thoughts on code, tech, and the digital world.</p>
      <div class="terminal-box">
        <span class="command-line">git config --global user.name</span>
        <span class="command-output">Salman Qureshi</span>
       </div>
    </div>

    <div class="open-source-card">
      <h3>Fork This Blog</h3>
      <p>OpLog is open source and developed by Salman Qureshi. You can clone it and create your own blog from your federated instance (Mastodon, Pleroma, or Akkoma).</p>
      <div class="terminal-box">
        <span class="command-line">git clone https://github.com/hotheadhacker/akkoma-blog.git</span>
        <span class="command-line">cd akkoma-blog</span>
        <span class="command-line">npm install</span>
        <span class="command-line">npm run start</span>
      </div>
      <a href="https://github.com/hotheadhacker/akkoma-blog" target="_blank" class="github-link">
        View on GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="activitypub-card">
      <h3>Federated Content</h3>
      <p>OpLog is powered by the ActivityPub protocol, the same technology behind the Fediverse. Posts are fetched directly from my Akkoma instance.</p>
      <a href="https://activitypub.rocks/" target="_blank" class="activitypub-link">Learn about ActivityPub</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="topics-card">
      <h3>Topics</h3>
      <ul class="topics-list">
        <li>Technology</li>
        <li>Programming</li>
        <li>Open Source</li>
        <li>Digital Privacy</li>
        <li>Web Development</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    </aside>
